<p class="wikiPara">
I'm proud to present the initial version of Fresh, CLI for JBossAS.
</p>

<p class="wikiPara">
This is definitely not the only CLI developed under our roof (<a href="http://anonsvn.jboss.org/repos/jbossas/branches/Branch_5_x/adminclient/" target="" class="regularLink">see adminclient repository</a>) but it brings a ton of interesting stuff developed by the people who donated it, my friends from <a href="http://www.parsek.si" target="" class="regularLink">Parsek</a> company, Tomaz Cerar and Marko Strukelj (yes, the one who's responsible for vfszip :-)).
</p>

<p class="wikiPara">
This is the JIRA release issue, where you can learn more about it,
download the deployable artifact, etc
